        "jsCode": "// Prepare the Data for the Real Backend API\n// Convert simple Bounds to GeoJSON Polygon\nconst bounds = $json.body.bounds || { north: 0, south: 0, east: 0, west: 0 };\n\nconst geometry = {\n  type: \"Polygon\",\n  coordinates: [[\n    [bounds.west, bounds.north],\n    [bounds.east, bounds.north],\n    [bounds.east, bounds.south],\n    [bounds.west, bounds.south],\n    [bounds.west, bounds.north]\n  ]]\n};\n\nreturn {\n  geometry: geometry\n};"
